\v 1 \w How|strong="H4100"\w* beautiful \w are|strong="H4100"\w* \w your|strong="H7725"\w* sandaled feet, princess!\f + \fr 7:1 \ft “Princess”: literally, “daughter of a noble.”\f* \w Your|strong="H7725"\w* curved thighs \w are|strong="H4100"\w* \w like|strong="H7725"\w* ornaments \w made|strong="H7725"\w* \w by|strong="H7725"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* master craftsman.
